#. Plugin Name of the plugin
msgid "Event Tickets with Ticket Scanner"
msgstr ""

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
msgid "https://vollstart.com/event-tickets-with-ticket-scanner/docs/"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"You can create and generate tickets and codes. You can redeem the tickets at "
"entrance using the built-in ticket scanner. You customer can download a PDF "
"with the ticket information. The Premium allows you also to activate user "
"registration and more. This allows your user to register them self to a "
"ticket."
msgstr ""
"Je kunt tickets en ticketnummers aanmaken en laten genereren. Je kunt de "
"tickets bij de ingang inwisselen met de ingebouwde ticketscanner. Je klanten "
"kunnen het ticket als PDF downloaden. Met de Premium-versie kun je ook de "
"registratie van kopers op het ticket en nog veel meer activeren."

#. Author of the plugin
